snippet.title: Play The Ascent Day One with Xbox Game Pass – Xbox & Bethesda Games Showcase 2021
snippet.description:
Play The Ascent day one on console, PC, and cloud with Xbox Game Pass on July 29, 2021.
https://www.xbox.com/games/the-ascent

The Ascent is a solo and co-op Action-shooter RPG set in a cyberpunk world. The mega corporation that owns you and everyone, The Ascent Group, has just collapsed. Can you survive without it?
 
Subscribe to Xbox 🎮 https://xbx.lv/2EEjmaR
